OL,3,CWhy the IFS thinks Labour and the
OL,4,CTories are being dishonest
OL,6,FThe IFS estimates day-to-day spending
OL,7,Ffor a range of departments outside
OL,8,Fhealth, defence and education, is fall
OL,9,Fby something like #20 billion a year
OL,10,Fby 2028/2029.
OL,12,FThe chancellor hasn't set out how
OL,13,Fthese cuts will be delivered.
OL,15,FLabour is not saying if it would
OL,16,Freverse them and, if it plans to, how
OL,17,Fit would find the money,
OL,19,F"Neither side is being transparent
OL,20,Fabout the challenges," Johnson said.
