OL,3,CWhy the IFS thinks Labour and the
OL,4,CTories are being dishonest
OL,6,FBoth parties say that they want to
OL,7,Fhave debt falling in the medium term
OL,8,Fwhich means, if they take office, they
OL,9,Fwill find their ability to borrow
OL,10,Frestricted.
OL,12,FNational debt is high and rising and
OL,13,Fwe are living, for now, in a world of
OL,14,Fpoor economic growth and higher
OL,15,Finterest rates.
OL,17,FYou have to be careful with
OL,18,Fcomparisons between the finances of
OL,19,Fgovernments and households but imagine
OL,20,Fyou have a mortgage and your mortgage
OL,21,Frate went up.
