OL,3,CWhy the IFS thinks Labour and the
OL,4,CTories are being dishonest
OL,6,FThe stock of national debt has risen
OL,7,Fby #800 billion in cash terms since
OL,8,FFebruary 2020, to #2,418 billion and
OL,9,Fit's projected to rise further.
OL,11,FOver the same period, the interest the
OL,12,Fgovernment pays on it debt has
OL,13,Fincreased from #35 billion a year to
OL,14,F#100 billion. That's almost three
OL,15,Ftimes what the government's annual
OL,16,Fspending on defence.
